text: 212 Warrior (also known as Wiro Sableng 212 and Wiro Sableng Pendekar Kapak Maut Naga Geni 212) is a 2018 Indonesian action fantasy comedy movie directed by Angga Dwimas Sasongko and was based on the Wiro Sableng series by Bastian Tito. It stars Vino G. Bastian, Sherina Munaf, Marsha Timothy, Happy Salma, Dwi Sasono, Yayan Ruhian and was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:2018 comedy movies Category:2018 action movies Category:2018 fantasy movies Category:Indonesian movies Category:Movies based on books Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Angga Dwimas Sasongko
